name: knowledge
trans: Knowledge is information or understanding that you get from learning.

name: limit
trans: A limit is a point that you cannot go beyond.

name: maintain
trans: To maintain means to keep something in good condition.

name: notice
trans: To notice means to see or become aware of something.

name: organize
trans: To organize means to plan or arrange things neatly.

name: participate
trans: To participate means to take part in something.

name: quality
trans: Quality means how good or bad something is.

name: reflect
trans: To reflect means to show or think deeply about something.

name: strength
trans: Strength means being strong or powerful.

name: transport
trans: To transport means to carry people or goods from one place to another.
